msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/story"
msgid " Winter war, the attack on Honkaniemi. It's a pity some of our tanks broke down on the way here, but we will counterattack anyway. The enemy breakthrough is a threat, and we have to attack now!\n\nGoal:\n - Take the village of Honkaniemi.\n - Close the salient."
msgstr " Guerra de Inverno, o ataque a Honkaniemi. É uma pena que alguns de nossos tanques tenham quebrado no caminho, mas contra-atacaremos assim mesmo. O avanço inimigo é uma ameaça, e temos de atacar agora!\n\nObjetivo:\n - Tome a aldeia de Honkaniemi.\n - Feche o saliente."

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/place"
msgid "Honkaniemi"
msgstr "Honkaniemi"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/date"
msgid "26 february, 1940"
msgstr "26 de fevereiro de 1940"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/outro_start"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/outro_completed"
msgid "Well done! The threat has been eliminated, Honkaniemi is ours once more!"
msgstr "Muito bem! A ameaça foi eliminada, Honkaniemi é novamente nossa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/outro_failed"
msgid "This defeat is hard to take. We have to regroup and try again!"
msgstr "Esta derrota é difícil de aceitar. Temos de nos reagrupar e tentar novamente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/outro_failed_hq"
msgid "Mission failed! - Enemy captured your HQ!"
msgstr "Missão fracassada! - O inimigo capturou o seu QG!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/mission_hq"
msgid "You must hold your field HQ!"
msgstr "Você deve manter o seu QG de campo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/mission_attack"
msgid "Capture the village!"
msgstr "Capture a aldeia!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/flag_capture_status"
msgid "Your soldiers secured %1%/7 Soviet positions!"
msgstr "Seus soldados asseguraram %1%/7 posições soviéticas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/narrator_start0"
msgid "Welcome to Karelia, Major! This is our field HQ. It has to remain ours at all times!"
msgstr "Bem-vindo à Carélia, Major! Este é o nosso QG de campo. Deve permanecer conosco o tempo todo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/narrator_start1"
msgid "Comrade, you are in command of this counterattack. Attack the enemy defenses and take the village!"
msgstr "Camarada, você está no comando deste contra-ataque. Ataque as defesas inimigas e tome a aldeia!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/narrator_start2"
msgid "The Soviets may have strong anti-tank defenses. Make sure you destroy all AT positions!"
msgstr "Os soviéticos podem ter fortes defesas antitanque. Certifique-se de destruir todas as posições AT!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/narrator_start3"
msgid "Begin securing the objectives, while we bring forward some reinforcements for you to deploy!"
msgstr "Comece a assegurar os objetivos, enquanto trazemos alguns reforços para você implantar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Asetoverit! Soviets are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr "Asetoverit! Os soviéticos estão perto do nosso QG de campo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "We must hold the command post! There can be no talk of retreat here!"
msgstr "Devemos manter nosso posto de comando! Nada de falar em retirada aqui!"

msgctxt "mission/single/03-fin_skirmish/1940_02-fin_honkaniemi/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request airstrikes."
msgstr "Major! Agora você pode solicitar ataques aéreos."
